{"tid":2501270,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國調高對澳門旅遊警示至「請勿前往」級別   反而香港只係「重新考慮前往 」","createTime":"2021-04-23T08:55:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T10:45:35.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"042208fe282291fce7e9122c8ba44bd90860f4cf","tid":2501270,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:55:29.000Z","msg":"【愛瞞報道】美國調高本澳旅遊警示「請勿前往」級別 提供資訊要求更正？ 衛生局：外國人不宜來澳<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院日前（20日）將本澳旅遊警示級別由第一級「採取正常預防措施」直接上調至第四級「請勿前往」，與朝鮮、坦桑尼亞等國家「睇齊」，反觀每日仍有感染個案的日本、澳洲、香港等地卻被分類為第三級「重新考慮前往 」。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院表示，調整旅遊警示主要是參考美國疾控中心（CDC）的健康預警。而據CDC網站資料，本澳新型冠狀病毒的分級為「未知級別（Unknown）」，並建議旅客應避免前往澳門。同樣處於「未知級別」的國家包括朝鮮、湯加、阿爾及利亞、坦桑尼亞、塔吉克斯坦等40多國。<br />\n<br />\n為此，《愛瞞》昨（22日）向衛生當局查詢會否向外界提供本澳疫情現況，更正相關旅遊警示，以證本澳是「安全宜遊」城市。衛生局僅回覆指「目前本澳對由外國來澳的非居民入境作出嚴格限制，不適合作為在外國人士的旅遊目的地。」又強調本澳疫情資訊公開透明。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/175341158_3877279119007827_7546339380967998830_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=973b4a&amp;_nc_ohc=a2CJskbProYAX_F3i06&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-2.xx&amp;oh=efc50d659c061c3913126bac5c34e0e4&amp;oe=60A8C5C6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.6435-9%2F175341158_3877279119007827_7546339380967998830_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26ccb%3D1-3%26_nc_sid%3D973b4a%26_nc_ohc%3Da2CJskbProYAX_F3i06%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-2.xx%26oh%3Defc50d659c061c3913126bac5c34e0e4%26oe%3D60A8C5C6&h=e5fd7ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-hk.facebook.com/macauconcealers/photos/a.158212900914486/3877279115674494\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-hk.facebook.com%2Fmacauconcealers%2Fphotos%2Fa.158212900914486%2F3877279115674494&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=378a9aa5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-hk.facebook.com/macauconcealers/photos/a.158212900914486/3877279115674494</a>"},{"pid":"0d8c04d2a4bf90d6e464d2ed0ff08ac258eb137f","tid":2501270,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:58:16.000Z","msg":"澳門冇事呀 感冒姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624664df9f1628f3e24f1529901be714e8fe5b7e","tid":2501270,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:58:33.000Z","msg":"是但啦<br />\n垃圾地方wfc"},{"pid":"ff50d3601b4740fa742ee97de2061611da51d38f","tid":2501270,"uid":198278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:59:27.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">隔離隻澳門狗唔敢入嚟認輸</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2c1749e3c54c01c78965f0064a6bc99aa0d812","tid":2501270,"uid":128102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:02:31.000Z","msg":"馬交夾人好撚易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26e74ce18b3b0a5c93c5246316304f6f9af76ec","tid":2501270,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff50d3601b4740fa742ee97de2061611da51d38f","tid":2501270,"uid":198278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:59:27.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">隔離隻澳門狗唔敢入嚟認輸</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:14:34.000Z","msg":"又輸"},{"pid":"615a978ce34142449238ca0e211c965ab1a6acb8","tid":2501270,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:22:06.000Z","msg":"仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n澳門只歡迎大陸人<br />\n<br />\n香港唔歡迎大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b72b5a21ab339cf6aa9b6cc17132e276a22e03","tid":2501270,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:45:35.000Z","msg":"美帝梗識分邊啲係假新聞啦<br />\n支那梗係有支那肺炎啦，仲去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}